| c1   | c2   |
+------+------+
|    1 |   10 |
|    2 |   20 |
|    3 |   30 |
|   10 |    1 |
|   10 |  100 |
|   20 |    2 |
|   20 |  200 |
|   30 |    3 |
|   90 |  900 |
|  100 |   10 |
|  200 |   20 |
|  900 |   90 |
